dialogue.speaker: Biff
dialogue.line: Marty, what are you doing here!?

dialogue.speaker: Marty
dialogue.line: Biff, I could not find any nice matches, but then I see this Lorraine|Chick on Timber, and now I am here!

dialogue.speaker: Biff
dialogue.line: Nah nah Marty, she is mine and I will not let you get to her!

dialogue.speaker: Marty
dialogue.line: I would like to see you try Frog Legs!
